- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a meta learning approach for reinforcement learning.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper addresses the problem of sample efficiency and exploration in reinforcement learning.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is mentioned in the paper as the task involves hitting a hockey puck to a target, which may require visual perception.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with controlling a robotic system.
